headline: HistoSonics’ histotripsy system receives early market access authorisation in UK
summary: The authorisation for the histotripsy system was granted under the UK’s Innovative Devices Access Pathway (IDAP).

headline: 3 Elite High-Yield Dividend Stocks Down 8% to 27% That Have Hiked Their Payouts for More than 50 Years in a Row
summary: Federal Realty has increased its dividend by a REIT-leading 57 straight years.  Johnson & Johnson has hiked its dividend for 63 years in a row.  PepsiCo recently extended its dividend growth streak to 53 consecutive years.
